data.author: NovAtel Applications Engineering
data.message:
ROS1 (#52)

* Add support for Honeywell HG4930 AN04 IMU

* Support for imu/data_raw topic, populated from RAWIMUSX log.
User must scale the data as described in RAWIMUSX documentation.

* Fix issue 46: output data in sensor frame as per REP145

* /imu/data_raw: output scaled data

* Supported IMU list: fix typos

* Adding PPPPOS, TERRASTARINFO, and TERRASTARSTATUS

Added ROS topic to publish PPPPOS, TERRASTARINFO, and TERRASTARSTATUS

* Fixed version number for package release

* Adding bestgnsspos handler (#45)

* Added bestgnsspos logs handler

Co-authored-by: NovAtel Applications Engineering <46907146+novatel-applications-engineering@users.noreply.github.com>

* Fixing RXSTATUS Handler and SolutionStatus.msg (#49)

* fixed SolutionStatus.msg

* Added receiver error flag to receiver_status_strs

* cherry-pick BESTGNSSPOS and RXSTATUS changes to ROS1

Co-authored-by: Joe Chen <joe.chen@hexagon.com>
Co-authored-by: ErtanSahinn <92147622+ErtanSahinn@users.noreply.github.com>
